                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-1017-18380402 t18380402-1017-punishment-90"></join>Confined Six Months</rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">THOMAS JONES</hi>—<hi rend="largeCaps">
                     <rs id="t18380402-1017-verdict-2" type="verdictDescription">
